EmailTemplate.name: Application closed - RFI
EmailTemplate.subject: Department of Licensing - We have closed your {!MUSW__License2__c.Credential_Type__c} license application.
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
We’ve closed your {!MUSW__License2__c.Credential_Type__c} license application.
We asked you for information or documents on {!MUSW__License2__c.RFI_Send_Date__c} and again on {!MUSW__License2__c.RFI_Send_Date_2nd__c}.
We didn’t receive it so we have closed your application.
If you want to get a license you must submit a new application with a new payment at {!MUSW__License2__c.Portal_URL__c}.
Questions? Need help? {!MUSW__License2__c.Application_Type__c} {!MUSW__License2__c.Program_Email__c} {!MUSW__License2__c.Program_Phone__c}
Thank you.
Department of Licensing www.dol.wa.gov GEN006
